Objective
	- Date Time API
	- Logical Exercise
	- Java-8 Exercise : Date Time
	
Date and Time API(Java-7)
	- java.util
	- Date, Calendar, SimpleDateFormat
	- Mutable
	- Complexity
	- No classes  provided to handle Time Zone
	
External API : Joda Time API

Java - 8 : 
	- java.time
	- lots and lots of methods for date manipulation
	- Immutable
	- Handle Time Zones

java.time
	- LocalDate
	- LocalTime
	- LocalDateTime
	- ZonedDateTime
	- DateTimeFormat
	- Duration
	- Period


















